textBeforeTable: Craft Size chart 30 days Manufacturer Warranty: cool weather road cycling Recommended Use: above ankle Height: [socks] 60% wool, 38% polyamide, 2% elastane Material: Tech Specs The Craft WARM Mid Socks are available in five sizes from X-Small to X-Large and in the color Black/bright red. Wool was applied in the heel, and at a majority of the sole, in order to provide the ultimate in warmth and insulation. This is what distinguishes the 'warm' line from the 'active' line, as the active collection omits wool in the sole. Craft finished off its WARM Mid socks with mid-length Lycra cuffs for added leg coverage and muscle support. The socks have been channel-stitched throughout, and they've received ultra-thin uppers. As a result, warm air is allowed to circulate in order cool down your skin temperature.
